    "attributes": {
        "action": "Permit leisure flying and allow flight schools to reopen.",
        "additional_details": "If pilots can\u2019t fly it takes away their pride and joy. Having this taken away from them for months on end can really affect some people. Student pilots who have paid for lessons have not been able to learn because the schools keep getting closed.\r\n \r\n",
        "background": "We want to government to let private/leisure pilots fly again and for them to reopen the flight schools because small planes like ours can\u2019t be left on the ground for months on end like big airliners can.",
